too will wake up.

01:12:06.400 --> 01:12:07.080
Maya!

01:12:08.360 --> 01:12:11.680
I know that every girl desires
her marriage to be conducted,

01:12:12.520 --> 01:12:14.080
..with great pomp and show.

01:12:15.080 --> 01:12:18.640
