Henna should adorn her hands.

01:12:21.000 --> 01:12:26.560
But you have to get married like this.
Secretly! Covertly!

01:12:29.400 --> 01:12:32.840
But Maya, if everybody's
desires got fulfilled,

01:12:33.640 --> 01:12:35.360
..then temples
wouldn't be built,

01:12:36.400 --> 01:12:37.960
..and nobody would
come here to pray.

01:12:39.800 --> 01:12:43.960
No, Prem. I have no
complains with God.

01:12:45.200 --> 01:12:48.560
I have no complains with you, too.
I'm angry at myself.

01:12:50.480 --> 01:12:53.160
Because of me, your image
is being tarnished.

01:12:56.480 --> 01:12:58.280
A self-respecting man like you,

01:12:59.000 --> 01:13:05.000
..has to secretly accept an
unfortunate female like me.

01:13:07.800 --> 01:13:13.320
Instead of my family's blessings
you'll only get their curses.

01:13:15.160 --> 01:13:16.320
Maya, you shouldn't say that.

01:13:17.160 --> 01:13:19.080
Elders do get annoyed
with children.

01:13:19.680 --> 01:13:20.960
But they never curse them.

01:13:24.720 --> 01:13:27.800
Your family will forget
all this very soon.

01:13:28.160 --> 01:13:29.680
They'll shower their
blessing on us.

01:13:31.840 --> 01:13:32.840
Prem. – Beat him!

01:13:33.160 --> 01:13:35.200
You come with me.
- Don't beat him!

01:13:35.720 --> 01:13:37.520
Want to do love marriage?

01:13:37.560 --> 01:13:40.080
Don't beat him!
- Keep quiet! Come!

01:13:41.800 --> 01:13:43.200
I’ll teach you a lesion.

01:13:44.120 --> 01:13:48.120
Please don't beat Prem! No!
Please don't beat Prem!

01:14:01.480 --> 01:14:02.320
Take this medicine.

01:14:06.680 --> 01:14:08.400
Take this medicine
and try to sleep.

01:14:09.800 --> 01:14:11.120
You need rest.

01:14:14.000 --> 01:14:14.400
Please.

01:14:15.320 --> 01:14:17.800
Have it. It'll flush out
the remaining poison.

01:14:19.680 --> 01:14:21.320
But I don't want to live.

01:14:23.840 --> 01:14:26.400
I don't have the courage
to lead dual lives.

01:14:29.600 --> 01:14:34.400
Get some poison for me.
I want to die.

01:14:34.840 --> 01:14:39.680
Look, I told you that I'm a doctor.
It's my profession to fight death.

01:14:41.200 --> 01:14:43.280
It's very easy to poison
somebody to death.

01:14:43.600 --> 01:14:45.480
But it's difficult to
save somebody from death.

01:14:47.280 --> 01:14:48.880
Death can't solve any problem.

01:14:50.480 --> 01:14:52.840
I won't pressurise you.

01:14:54.320 --> 01:14:56.720
But I too have a problem.

01:14:58.000 --> 01:15:01.400
Hear it out. Then you can
do whatever you want.

01:15:07.000 --> 01:15:10.680
Shanta, my first wife, died
while giving birth to Chanda.

01:15:13.600 --> 01:15:15.320
Her photo is still in this room.

01:15:16.480 --> 01:15:18.680
This is proof enough
that I still love her.

01:15:20.480 --> 01:15:24.160
She died 6 years ago. But
I didn't marry again.

01:15:26.640 --> 01:15:28.480
My mother was very
worried for me.

01:15:29.480 --> 01:15:33.640
Gradually this sorrow took a toll on
her health and she got bedridden.

01:15:35.720 --> 01:15:39.680
She had only one wish. She
wanted a daughter-in-law.

01:15:41.080 --> 01:15:43.720
So that the motherless
Chanda gets a mother.

01:15:47.480 --> 01:15:49.280
You've seen how ill mother is.

01:15:52.120 --> 01:15:55.640
As a son, I want my mother
to live a long life.

01:15:57.600 --> 01:16:03.400
But as a doctor, I know that she
won't live for more than a few days.

01:16:05.840 --> 01:16:10.080
I agreed to get married to
give some happiness to,

01:16:10.200 --> 01:16:11.680
..my mother during
her last days.

01:16:14.480 --> 01:16:16.800
When mother applied
vermillion on your forehead,

01:16:19.120 --> 01:16:21.320
I saw the joy on her face.

01:16:24.120 --> 01:16:26.960
I hadn't seen such happiness on
mother's face for the past 6 years.

01:16:29.840 --> 01:16:31.480
I know that I'll never
get to see it again.

01:16:35.080 --> 01:16:38.400
In order not to hurt my
mother during her last days,

01:16:39.680 --> 01:16:47.680
I request you to live in this
house for a few days, as my wife.

01:16:48.160 --> 01:16:51.960
I promise you that
I'll find your Prem.

01:16:52.800 --> 01:16:54.800
I'll hand you over
to him respectfully.

01:17:00.000 --> 01:17:03.840
I don't want you to
stay here forcefully.

01:17:05.480 --> 01:17:09.800
If you live as my
wife for a few days,

01:17:11.000 --> 01:17:12.520
I'll forever remain
indebted to you.

01:17:18.400 --> 01:17:20.840
I hope you'll think
calmly about this,

01:17:20.880 --> 01:17:22.840
..and reach the right
decision by morning.

01:17:25.720 --> 01:17:28.080
I'll take leave now. Goodnight!

01:17:43.120 --> 01:17:46.720
Dad! Grandpa said that from today
my new mother will look after me!

01:17:46.800 --> 01:17:48.400
Then why are you
giving me a bath?

01:17:50.160 --> 01:17:52.120
Dear, this house is
new for your new mom.

01:17:53.080 --> 01:17:55.000
She doesn't even know
where the bathroom is,

01:17:55.600 --> 01:17:59.160
..where the soap is, where
Chanda's clothes are.

01:18:00.360 --> 01:18:02.800
After she learns all this,
she'll look after you.

01:18:03.640 --> 01:18:05.480
Don't trouble your new mom.

01:18:06.800 --> 01:18:10.800
First find out whether she's
in a good mood. - But...

01:18:12.480 --> 01:18:14.800
But why will her
mood be bad, dad?

01:18:15.720 --> 01:18:19.480
I've brought her here away
from her home, her mother.

01:18:20.480 --> 01:18:21.880
So she must be missing them.

01:18:22.840 --> 01:18:27.320
I see! Then send new mom
back to her house, dad!

01:18:28.680 --> 01:18:32.800
I'll send her, dear. In a week or
so, I'll send her back to her home.

01:18:46.800 --> 01:18:47.560
How are you feeling now?

01:18:51.560 --> 01:18:52.680
You didn't take the tablets.

01:18:54.080 --> 01:18:55.920
Please don't be careless.

01:18:56.320 --> 01:18:57.920
You've to take it twice, in
the morning and evening.

01:18:58.800 --> 01:19:01.480
I'm going to the hospital.
I'll find out about him.

01:19:02.200 --> 01:19:03.680
He must be somewhere
in the city.

01:19:03.760 --> 01:19:08.000
We'll find him and all your
problems will be solved.

01:19:09.320 --> 01:19:09.800
I'm leaving.

01:19:20.840 --> 01:19:22.920
I have a small request.

01:19:24.800 --> 01:19:28.480
Mother must be eagerly waiting
for her daughter-in-law.

01:19:29.120 --> 01:19:31.360
If not as a daughter-in-law,
then for the sake of humanity,

01:19:32.120 --> 01:19:36.520
..if you sit with my dying
mother for sometime,

01:19:37.520 --> 01:19:38.800
I'll be indebted to you.

01:19:54.000 --> 01:19:55.480
What is this, son?

01:19:56.400 --> 01:19:59.120
It hasn't been a day since your marriage,
and you're going to the hospital?

01:19:59.840 --> 01:20:02.800
What will that poor girl think?

01:20:02.880 --> 01:20:05.400
It's important to go, father. I
have to perform 2-3 operations.

01:20:07.000 --> 01:20:08.800
Why should the patients suffer
because of my marriage?

01:20:10.000 --> 01:20:11.320
Why to put their life in danger?

01:20:15.800 --> 01:20:21.400
Anand, you refused for 6 years.

01:20:22.520 --> 01:20:27.000
But you've finally married again
for the sake of your mother.

01:20:28.560 --> 01:20:32.000
Because I won't live for long.
Am I right?

01:20:32.280 --> 01:20:35.000
Don't say that, mother.
You're getting better.

01:20:36.080 --> 01:20:40.800
In a week's time you'll
start walking, too.

01:20:41.320 --> 01:20:46.080
Talk to your mother like a
son, not like a doctor.

01:20:48.000 --> 01:20:50.800
Tell me. Did you like the girl?

01:20:51.840 --> 01:20:55.200
She's good. She was
about to come down.

01:20:55.280 --> 01:20:59.160
She saw some books lying around.
So she started arranging them.

01:21:00.000 --> 01:21:01.600
She'll come to meet you
after taking a bath.

01:21:03.480 --> 01:21:09.000
Have you both gelled well? Have
you both liked each other?

01:21:11.080 --> 01:21:11.520
Yes.

01:21:12.560 --> 01:21:18.400
Son, I know that you can
never forget Shanta.

01:21:21.000 --> 01:21:25.320
I don't say that you should
forget people after their death.

01:21:28.000 --> 01:21:30.600
But you should not
hurt those who're,

01:21:30.680 --> 01:21:32.280
..alive by mourning
for the deceased.

01:21:32.720 --> 01:21:34.000
What have I done, mother?

01:21:40.840 --> 01:21:46.680
Promise that you'll
always keep her happy.

01:21:47.800 --> 01:21:50.920
Promise me. - Yes, mother.

01:21:51.480 --> 01:21:53.200
I'll do everything for
Maya's happiness.

01:21:54.720 --> 01:21:57.720
I promise you that I'll
fulfil all her wishes.

01:21:59.400 --> 01:22:02.200
I heard that day before, a
couple came here to get married.

01:22:02.280 --> 01:22:03.200
Yes. I'm asking about them.

01:22:04.000 --> 01:22:06.800
Can you tell me where that guy is?
- I told you. I don't know anything.

01:22:07.520 --> 01:22:11.000
Kishan! Was there a
fight here that night?

01:22:11.520 --> 01:22:15.200
Sir, it was great! They bought
two garlands from my shop!

01:22:15.400 --> 01:22:16.720
That guy was a Punjabi!

01:22:17.160 --> 01:22:22.320
Look at his guts! He was flirting
with a girl from my locality!

01:22:22.520 --> 01:22:26.240
People thrashed him
black and blue!

01:22:26.320 --> 01:22:28.640
I quietly watched
from behind the door.

01:22:29.200 --> 01:22:32.800
Nowadays people shouldn't interfere
in all this. - Then what happened?

01:22:32.840 --> 01:22:35.920
Sir, I fled. Who'd want to
get involved with the law?

01:22:40.800 --> 01:22:44.520
Wait! I'll answer it! Go!

01:22:45.200 --> 01:22:47.400
Hello! This is Chanda
Anand speaking!

01:22:47.800 --> 01:22:51.000
Hello, Ms. Anand. This is Dr.
Anand speaking.

01:22:51.360 --> 01:22:52.320
Yes, doctor.

01:22:52.400 --> 01:22:54.560
Did mom have her breakfast?
- No!

01:22:56.000 --> 01:22:59.520
No? Did she have her medicine?
- No!

01:23:00.480 --> 01:23:04.320
Did she go down to meet grandma?
- No!

01:23:05.400 --> 01:23:06.480
I see!

01:23:07.720 --> 01:23:08.200
Listen, dear.

01:23:09.360 --> 01:23:13.600
Tell mom it's fine if she doesn't
want to go to meet grandma.

01:23:13.680 --> 01:23:15.720
But ask her to take her medicine.
Fine?

01:23:17.000 --> 01:23:20.840
Oh! I see!

01:23:44.040 --> 01:23:49.240
Dad called up and said its okay if
you don't want to meet grandma.

01:23:49.400 --> 01:23:53.120
But have your breakfast and
do take your medicine.

01:23:53.160 --> 01:23:54.640
That is most important.

01:24:22.320 --> 01:24:25.080
'Mother must be eagerly waiting
for her daughter-in-law.'

01:24:26.120 --> 01:24:28.320
'If not as a daughter-in-law,
for the sake of humanity,'

01:24:28.800 --> 01:24:32.120
'if you sit with my dying
mother for sometime,'

01:24:32.520 --> 01:24:33.600
'I'll be indebted to you.'

01:24:43.200 --> 01:24:44.600
Did you like this house, dear?

01:24:46.800 --> 01:24:49.080
And my son?

01:24:52.000 --> 01:24:53.600
Did he talk to you?

01:24:56.800 --> 01:24:59.120
His nature is a bit
different, dear.

01:24:59.760 --> 01:25:05.240
He doesn't talk too much.
Don't feel disappointed. Ok?

01:25:13.000 --> 01:25:16.480
The honour, respect, peace
and harmony of this house,

01:25:17.480 --> 01:25:19.920
I'm handing over
everything to you, dear.

01:25:21.600 --> 01:25:25.480
The day I had come in this
house as a daughter-in-law,

01:25:25.800 --> 01:25:29.760
..my mother-in-law had given
me this responsibility.

01:25:30.400 --> 01:25:32.480
I'm doing the same thing today.

01:25:37.680 --> 01:25:43.080
Though you're young,
but from today,

01:25:43.600 --> 01:25:45.800
I'm giving you the responsibility
of three children.

01:25:46.640 --> 01:25:49.160
Father, son and granddaughter.

01:25:49.840 --> 01:25:52.800
You'll have to be the
mother of all three.

01:25:57.080 --> 01:26:01.200
Anand didn't marry for
6 years fearing that,

01:26:02.160 --> 01:26:06.080
..maybe the step-mother won't
take good care of the child.

01:26:07.400 --> 01:26:10.600
But I judged you at first sight.

01:26:11.560 --> 01:26:13.200
That you are not
such kind of a girl.

01:26:14.800 --> 01:26:19.160
Promise me dear, that
you'll look after Chanda.

01:26:22.080 --> 01:26:26.480
I knew that you'll
be kind at heart.

01:26:27.800 --> 01:26:32.160
Your arrival will bring back
the happiness of this house.

01:26:40.200 --> 01:26:42.360
Mom, dad had called again!

01:26:43.000 --> 01:26:45.320
He was asking whether
mom had her breakfast.

01:26:45.400 --> 01:26:48.520
I said mom hasn't even
touched her breakfast.

01:26:48.840 --> 01:26:50.960
So dad said, I see!

01:26:51.280 --> 01:26:54.520
So Chanda, tell mother
to have her breakfast.

01:26:57.120 --> 01:26:59.360
I can't eat so much!

01:27:00.000 --> 01:27:03.000
The other plate is mine, mom.

01:27:03.280 --> 01:27:07.200
I thought if I eat,
you won't eat at all.

01:27:07.320 --> 01:27:08.800
So I too didn't eat.

01:27:09.200 --> 01:27:12.080
If I starved my whole life
will you do the same?

01:27:12.200 --> 01:27:17.320
Yes! But mom, I'm famished!
- Is that so? Come!

01:27:23.320 --> 01:27:25.120
You are very sweet, mom!

01:27:27.400 --> 01:27:29.200
Now you eat, mom! - Okay.

01:28:25.200 --> 01:28:25.800
Maya!

01:28:27.320 --> 01:28:31.400
Chotu will wake up! - Boss, I won't
wake up. I'm in deep slumber.

01:28:32.720 --> 01:28:36.360
He's talking in his sleep.
- Yes. I'm talking in my sleep, boss.

01:28:36.840 --> 01:28:39.360
Leave! - C'mon!

01:28:39.440 --> 01:28:41.640
What? What are you doing?
Leave my hand!

01:28:41.760 --> 01:28:43.800
Otherwise I'll raise commotion!
- What commotion?

01:28:44.000 --> 01:28:46.080
My honour is at stake!
Won't I raise a commotion?

01:28:47.080 --> 01:28:50.400
Then shout! Whom will you call?
Chotu?

01:28:50.520 --> 01:28:52.400
Why have you come up alone
so late in the night?

01:28:52.600 --> 01:28:55.000
Should I bring grandpa along?
Fool!

01:28:55.120 --> 01:28:59.600
Fool? Have you come at midnight
to tell me that I'm a fool?

01:28:59.720 --> 01:29:03.400
Then what! Guys plead so much!

01:29:03.480 --> 01:29:07.360
They implore so much! Only then
does the girl agree to meet!

01:29:07.840 --> 01:29:11.160
Does a girl come all
alone at night?

01:29:11.520 --> 01:29:12.280
Then why have you come?

01:29:14.080 --> 01:29:17.000
I've been mad enough to
fall in love with you.

01:29:17.600 --> 01:29:20.080
Had it been some other guy then...
- What would he do?

01:29:21.320 --> 01:29:23.120
He would take advantage
of this opportunity.

01:29:26.480 --> 01:29:28.160
It's a cold moonlit night.

01:29:29.000 --> 01:29:37.400
We should hold each
others hands and romance.

01:29:41.800 --> 01:29:45.360
Talk romantically now!
- Oh my God!

01:29:46.200 --> 01:29:50.600
Look, I've already
crossed my line.

01:29:51.120 --> 01:29:53.920
Now if we are caught, we'll
be thrashed black and blue.

01:29:55.080 --> 01:29:57.040
We won't be thrashed any
less if we sit apart.

01:29:57.600 --> 01:30:00.520
Sitting close won't help us escape
a good thrashing as well. Got it?

01:30:01.320 --> 01:30:03.880
What should I do now?

01:30:04.560 --> 01:30:10.800
Now you'll place your
head on my lap and rest.

01:30:12.000 --> 01:30:18.000
No! Not on your lap.
- Look! Just do what I say!

01:30:18.640 --> 01:30:22.720
Otherwise I'll scream
and tell every one,

01:30:23.080 --> 01:30:29.160
..that you called me here and
you're trying to rape me.

01:30:29.240 --> 01:30:32.840
No! - Now quietly lie down here!

01:30:40.480 --> 01:30:42.000
This is my knee, not my lap!

01:30:44.800 --> 01:30:46.000
Now turn your face!

01:30:51.560 --> 01:30:52.760
What happened?

01:30:53.520 --> 01:30:56.320
Maya, I'm telling you!
Go away otherwise...

01:30:56.400 --> 01:30:58.000
Otherwise what?
- You'll catch cold!

01:30:58.200 --> 01:31:01.000
You could catch cold if you stayed
out in the moonlit night for long!

01:31:09.880 --> 01:31:11.200
Sit properly!

01:31:14.120 --> 01:31:16.960
Tell me! - Kiss me!

01:31:17.160 --> 01:31:18.640
What? - A kiss!

01:31:21.520 --> 01:31:24.600
No, Maya! - Yes fool!

01:31:26.400 --> 01:31:30.720
Look, if you don't kiss me,
I'll stay here the whole night.

01:31:32.520 --> 01:31:32.920
Kiss me!

01:31:36.400 --> 01:31:39.320
Where? - Kiss me here!

01:31:39.400 --> 01:31:42.120
No. – Its fine. Do it here.

01:31:44.080 --> 01:31:47.520
Will you leave if I kiss you?

01:31:48.160 --> 01:31:51.680
First kiss me, I'll think about it!
- Then I won't kiss you!

01:31:51.840 --> 01:31:53.720
Fine! Give me a kiss!

01:31:54.200 --> 01:31:54.920
Look at your face!

01:32:00.320 --> 01:32:05.800
Are you loving me or drinking poison!
Smile!

01:32:19.000 --> 01:32:22.800
Is this a smile!
Do it with style!

01:32:34.160 --> 01:32:34.920
Maya!

01:32:35.720 --> 01:32:38.520
Now the boss will be thrashed!

01:32:41.720 --> 01:32:47.080
Father! Get up! Look!
Maya is not in her bed!

01:32:47.160 --> 01:32:49.840
Look down. Maybe she
fell down in her sleep.

01:32:49.880 --> 01:32:53.520
Don't joke, father! I'm worried!

01:32:53.840 --> 01:32:59.920
Don't worry. She's not a kid. I
mean she must be in the bathroom.

01:33:00.000 --> 01:33:02.240
Go and find her! This
house is not a Taj Mahal!

01:33:02.720 --> 01:33:05.920
Go! - How do I go? Mother
is standing down there.

01:33:06.120 --> 01:33:07.320
Then go from here!

01:33:14.000 --> 01:33:17.160
Climb down! - How? Shall I jump?

01:33:17.200 --> 01:33:19.360
Jump! - Jump!?

01:33:20.720 --> 01:33:23.640
I'll break my bones? - Grandpa is
going to break your bones anyway.

01:33:24.600 --> 01:33:28.760
Father! She's not in the bathroom too!
God knows where she has gone!

01:33:28.840 --> 01:33:31.320
She is not a child to get lost!

01:33:31.480 --> 01:33:33.200
Search properly! She
must be here only. Go!

01:33:36.160 --> 01:33:36.840
What are you doing?

01:33:49.720 --> 01:33:50.800
Why are you looking
at me like this?

01:33:53.840 --> 01:33:56.200
Aren't you ashamed! My
honour is at stake!

01:33:56.280 --> 01:33:58.120
What are you doing? I'll die!

01:33:59.520 --> 01:34:01.360
You are not even
telling me to stay.

01:34:01.440 --> 01:34:05.240
Let mother come! Let
any storm arrive!

01:34:05.800 --> 01:34:10.360
I can fight the whole world!
Just hold my hands!

01:34:10.480 --> 01:34:12.000
Right now you are
holding my wraparound.

01:34:16.200 --> 01:34:17.760
Has Maya gone up?

01:34:17.840 --> 01:34:22.080
She must have gone to dry chillies.
- Are chillies dried at night?

01:34:22.720 --> 01:34:26.560
You mean to say that guy from
Patiala That music director!

01:34:26.840 --> 01:34:31.200
He's a young guy. Maya is a child.
Did that loafer entice her?

01:34:31.480 --> 01:34:35.320
I'll thrash that ***! You go up!

01:34:35.440 --> 01:34:37.000
I can't climb the
stairs in this old age!

01:34:49.000 --> 01:34:49.760
Maya!

01:34:51.720 --> 01:34:56.000
My wraparound! Give my wraparound!
- Don't shout!

01:34:56.400 --> 01:35:02.320
My wraparound! Give my wraparound!
Throw it up!

01:35:03.000 --> 01:35:06.160
Where are you taking my wraparound?
Give it back!

01:35:10.440 --> 01:35:14.000
Oh my God! Why did I see this?

01:35:24.480 --> 01:35:26.120
Doctor! - Yes, sister.

01:35:26.480 --> 01:35:29.120
I've called all the hospitals
and nursing homes.

01:35:29.240 --> 01:35:32.360
Mr. Prem has not been
admitted anywhere. - I see!

01:35:37.080 --> 01:35:41.360
Sister, do one thing. Call up all
the charitable homes and lodges.

01:35:43.000 --> 01:35:43.920
He must be somewhere.

01:35:44.840 --> 01:35:46.720
I'm very happy today, dear!

01:35:47.680 --> 01:35:51.120
It's a full moon day today
and a Thursday too.

01:35:52.840 --> 01:35:55.600
The priest says that today
