such a background music that,

02:00:38.160 --> 02:00:39.640
..everybody will tear up.

02:00:39.840 --> 02:00:42.560
I'll play it. Come on, Chotu!
Pick up the drum!

02:00:42.800 --> 02:00:44.160
Look, this is a sad tune.

02:00:44.760 --> 02:00:47.920
I'll thrash you if you laugh. Got it?
- Fine.

02:00:50.000 --> 02:00:52.920
Not so fast. Play it slowly.

02:01:12.400 --> 02:01:14.000
Boss! Boss!

02:01:15.200 --> 02:01:16.720
The producer is crying.

02:01:25.680 --> 02:01:27.400
This is the effect of our tune.

02:01:28.600 --> 02:01:30.280
I've only played the harmonium.

02:01:30.720 --> 02:01:33.280
Watch the effect when it's
played with 50 piece orchestra.

02:01:33.400 --> 02:01:36.280
Each person in the theatre will cry.
Come on!

02:03:07.680 --> 02:03:10.000
Prem Pratap from Patiala!
Music director!

02:03:10.480 --> 02:03:13.120
Hello, Mr. Prem.
- Greetings, sir.

02:03:14.080 --> 02:03:18.760
I was waiting for you since morning.
- Do one thing.

02:03:19.480 --> 02:03:21.840
Take a cab and come to
my house immediately.

02:03:22.800 --> 02:03:27.160
The address is Savitri villa.
10th Road, Juhu Parle Scheme.

02:03:27.280 --> 02:03:28.400
I'll come immediately, sir.

02:03:28.760 --> 02:03:31.840
But at least tell me. What have
you decided about the climax?

02:03:33.040 --> 02:03:35.800
Mr. Prem, I'll decide the climax
after taking your opinion.

02:03:36.640 --> 02:03:37.600
So please come here immediately.

02:03:40.840 --> 02:03:42.640
Dad, what is a climax?

02:03:46.320 --> 02:03:50.160
Separating two bodies
and uniting two souls.

02:03:57.200 --> 02:03:58.400
Greetings! - Greetings!

02:03:59.000 --> 02:04:00.160
I've come to meet Mr. Anand.

02:04:00.440 --> 02:04:02.400
Prem Pratap from Patiala.
Music director.

02:04:02.480 --> 02:04:03.200
Come, have a seat.

02:04:16.480 --> 02:04:19.560
The producer is rich.
He's an influential man.

02:04:21.400 --> 02:04:24.120
He'll surely complete the movie
by selling his house if needed.

02:04:27.800 --> 02:04:30.800
Sit. You've reached
the right place.

02:04:52.400 --> 02:04:53.720
Greetings, sir! - Greetings!

02:04:54.800 --> 02:04:56.160
I was waiting for you.

02:04:58.080 --> 02:05:04.320
Sir, you look tired. Are you fine?
- Yes. Just like that. Come.

02:05:05.000 --> 02:05:07.800
I understand, sir. I
understand your dilemma.

02:05:08.400 --> 02:05:11.600
When a man is in deep thought
and he can't decide anything,

02:05:12.000 --> 02:05:14.080
..he feels distressed.
- Come. Sit down.

02:05:14.480 --> 02:05:16.960
To tell you the truth. I'm too
thinking about the climax.

02:05:18.600 --> 02:05:21.000
I can't even eat properly.
- Please sit.

02:05:22.680 --> 02:05:24.480
Then you must have
reached some conclusion.

02:05:25.720 --> 02:05:27.640
What should be the climax of
this story according to you?

02:05:28.600 --> 02:05:31.320
Look, sir. There are only
two ends to this story.

02:05:31.840 --> 02:05:35.560
One is that the heroine
forgets her lover and,

02:05:35.720 --> 02:05:38.800
..spends her life happily
with her husband.

02:05:39.120 --> 02:05:40.800
The happy ending.

02:05:41.720 --> 02:05:46.400
The other end is that the
heroine forgets her,

02:05:46.800 --> 02:05:48.480
..lover and her husband
and leaves this world.

02:05:49.200 --> 02:05:52.400
Again she consumes poison.
The sad ending.

02:05:53.320 --> 02:05:56.800
Mr. Prem, I think you're
a heartless man. - What?

02:05:57.200 --> 02:06:01.000
You're forcing that girl to
spend her life with a man,

02:06:01.120 --> 02:06:04.120
..she married
against her wishes.

02:06:05.560 --> 02:06:10.080
This is injustice! This
happens in all the movies.

02:06:11.400 --> 02:06:15.000
Secondly, why should she
consume poison again?

02:06:16.160 --> 02:06:17.120
What is her fault?

02:06:19.840 --> 02:06:24.360
But sir, there can't be a third
climax to this story. - Why not?

02:06:25.840 --> 02:06:30.480
If that husband is a noble man, he
can unite the separated lovers.

02:06:31.000 --> 02:06:33.640
No, sir! That's
absolutely wrong!

02:06:34.600 --> 02:06:35.960
Even I thought of this.

02:06:36.240 --> 02:06:39.400
But people won't accept this climax.
- Why?

02:06:39.760 --> 02:06:45.720
Because sir, we have some
tradition, values and feelings.

02:06:46.720 --> 02:06:51.160
According to that, once a
man marries a woman and,

02:06:52.000 --> 02:06:54.600
..gives her the nuptial thread,
then she belongs to him.

02:06:55.000 --> 02:06:58.640
That woman becomes his wife
for the rest of her life.

02:06:59.480 --> 02:07:03.800
Once the 7 nuptial rounds of the
fire are taken with the oath,

02:07:04.080 --> 02:07:05.560
..it can't be broken.

02:07:06.160 --> 02:07:08.800
If 2 people married
according to the rituals,

02:07:09.400 --> 02:07:11.280
..can't maintain the
relation for some reason,

02:07:11.840 --> 02:07:15.000
..then the law gives them the
permission to seek divorce.

02:07:15.680 --> 02:07:19.400
Foreigners resort to a divorce, sir!
We are Indians!

02:07:20.240 --> 02:07:22.320
In our country, a
woman has to spend,

02:07:22.440 --> 02:07:24.400
..her life only with her
husband once marriage.

02:07:26.160 --> 02:07:29.480
So Mr. Prem, why doesn't this rule
apply on the men of our country?

02:07:30.800 --> 02:07:33.000
Even after marriage, many
marry for the second time,

02:07:33.080 --> 02:07:36.360
..or have extra-marital affairs.

02:07:37.200 --> 02:07:40.640
Then how does your tradition and
value accept them in the society?

02:07:42.360 --> 02:07:46.240
Why only women have to
obey the marriage rituals?

02:07:46.440 --> 02:07:51.240
Why not men?
- Sir, you have confused me.

02:07:52.800 --> 02:07:54.280
You have put me in a dilemma.

02:07:57.320 --> 02:07:58.800
My intention was not to
put you in a dilemma,

02:07:58.880 --> 02:08:01.000
..but to solve this problem.
Sit.

02:08:03.160 --> 02:08:06.160
Killing that girl or
forcing her to live,

02:08:06.440 --> 02:08:13.840
..with someone she doesn't
love is sinful! It's wrong.

02:08:15.400 --> 02:08:20.760
The right thing to do is to unite
that girl with her lover again.

02:08:22.400 --> 02:08:24.920
Am I right? - Okay.

02:08:26.000 --> 02:08:27.240
Very good, sir!

02:08:28.400 --> 02:08:32.600
Are you saying it for my sake or
do you really think so? - No, sir!

02:08:33.240 --> 02:08:36.280
You've explained everything
so clearly that,

02:08:36.720 --> 02:08:37.800
I think this is the
right thing to do.

02:08:38.840 --> 02:08:42.160
It will be a new climax.
Novelty!

02:08:42.320 --> 02:08:45.160
Very good, sir! It
will be revolutionary!

02:08:45.360 --> 02:08:47.160
People won't even be able
to think of this climax!

02:08:51.120 --> 02:08:52.480
Good that you agreed with me.

02:08:54.400 --> 02:08:56.120
Come upstairs.

02:08:59.000 --> 02:08:59.280
Upstairs?

02:09:01.560 --> 02:09:06.120
You have given your consent. Now
let me fulfil my duty too. Come.

02:09:06.280 --> 02:09:09.560
Sir, do you mean
advance payment?

02:09:10.240 --> 02:09:14.520
Yes! Assume it's an advance.
Come.

02:09:17.360 --> 02:09:21.480
Advance? Good! Very good, sir!

02:09:22.240 --> 02:09:25.360
You have thought of a fine climax!
Very good!

02:09:26.520 --> 02:09:29.000
Lovely story! Unexpected twists!

02:09:29.800 --> 02:09:31.560
Your movie is a hit!

02:09:32.280 --> 02:09:34.800
With Goddess Saraswati's grace,

02:09:35.280 --> 02:09:36.560
..the music will complete
a silver jubilee.

02:09:37.160 --> 02:09:41.080
Why silver jubilee?
Golden jubilee, sir!

02:09:41.600 --> 02:09:44.000
Sir, it has really been
a pleasure meeting you!

02:09:44.640 --> 02:09:47.720
What character! What a
theme for the story, sir!

02:09:47.840 --> 02:09:48.800
Wonderful! Beautiful...

02:10:09.280 --> 02:10:10.200
I'm sorry, Mr. Prem.

02:10:12.000 --> 02:10:13.960
But if I had told
you this earlier,

02:10:14.800 --> 02:10:15.760
..that Maya is the girl
who had consumed poison,

02:10:15.840 --> 02:10:17.560
..on the first night
of the wedding,

02:10:19.480 --> 02:10:21.440
..and that I am her husband,

02:10:22.640 --> 02:10:24.200
..we wouldn't have been
able to talk clearly.

02:10:25.480 --> 02:10:27.000
We would've never been able
to reach the right decision.

02:10:28.200 --> 02:10:29.600
That's why I had to
play this drama.

02:10:31.680 --> 02:10:35.960
Forgive me if I have hurt you.

02:10:40.360 --> 02:10:44.320
Maya, I'm fulfilling my promise.

02:10:46.720 --> 02:10:48.160
Though for my own
selfish reasons,

02:10:50.200 --> 02:10:56.120
I made you stay in this house for 7
days. I'm sorry for hurting you.

02:11:00.160 --> 02:11:02.600
The sad story that began
with this marriage,

02:11:04.000 --> 02:11:06.400
..has now become the happy
story of two lovers' union.

02:11:06.600 --> 02:11:10.800
I'm happy. My best
wishes are with you.

02:11:11.720 --> 02:11:16.240
Goodbye! Good luck! - Sir! Sir!

02:11:18.400 --> 02:11:19.360
This isn't right!

02:11:19.480 --> 02:11:22.320
Your climax is not right! It's wrong!
- Why?

02:11:23.280 --> 02:11:24.960
Just a while ago you
only had accepted it.

02:11:25.000 --> 02:11:29.200
Yes! Everything is fair in movies.
But this is real life.

02:11:29.840 --> 02:11:32.280
Such endings can't
happen in life, sir!

02:11:32.400 --> 02:11:36.200
But Mr. Prem, stories,
novels, movies,

02:11:37.160 --> 02:11:38.920
..all this should
portray real life.

02:11:39.120 --> 02:11:41.400
I don't want to argue whether they
should or shouldn't portray life.

02:11:42.400 --> 02:11:45.080
I accepted your climax because

02:11:45.240 --> 02:11:47.800
I didn't want to lose my chance
of being a music director.

02:11:48.720 --> 02:11:51.400
Otherwise I can never accept
such a derogatory thing.

02:11:52.680 --> 02:11:57.400
Maya is your wife. She has
to spend her life with you.

02:11:59.200 --> 02:12:01.560
But how do I accept your climax, Mr.
Prem?

02:12:03.320 --> 02:12:05.720
Knowing that the girl who
has come in my house,

02:12:06.640 --> 02:12:07.920
..as my wife loves
somebody else.

02:12:09.400 --> 02:12:09.920
She loves you.

02:12:12.280 --> 02:12:14.920
I can't torment myself
by making her my wife.

02:12:17.280 --> 02:12:20.160
Life will become hell. For
me as well as for Maya.

02:12:21.560 --> 02:12:25.760
There's only one solution to this
problem. Take Maya with you.

02:12:27.200 --> 02:12:31.480
No, sir. This isn't possible.

02:12:32.320 --> 02:12:35.200
If you will leave her here, she'll
surely consume poison again.

02:12:35.800 --> 02:12:36.760
Will that be acceptable to you?

02:12:39.200 --> 02:12:43.960
Can you let your beloved die?

02:12:45.000 --> 02:12:48.160
What kind of a man are you?
What kind of a lover are you?

02:12:59.360 --> 02:13:01.200
Fine, sir.

02:13:02.640 --> 02:13:04.480
I'll take Maya with me.

02:13:06.080 --> 02:13:07.160
But not this Maya,

02:13:09.000 --> 02:13:13.160
..return the same Maya, I
had fallen in love with.

02:13:13.440 --> 02:13:18.160
Mr. Prem, do you doubt me? - No,
sir! I am not such a stooped man!

02:13:18.520 --> 02:13:19.600
I'll never doubt you!

02:13:19.720 --> 02:13:25.200
I mean to say that Maya is wearing
the nuptial thread given by you.

02:13:26.160 --> 02:13:29.600
If I touch her, I'll feel as
if I am committing a sin.

02:13:30.200 --> 02:13:32.840
As if I have brought home
somebody else's wife.

02:13:34.600 --> 02:13:38.680
If this nuptial thread is
removed, I'll get my Maya back.

02:13:40.560 --> 02:13:46.080
Maya, give this nuptial thread back
to the doctor and come with me.

02:13:52.800 --> 02:13:53.640
What happened, Maya?

02:13:54.800 --> 02:13:57.080
A nuptial thread is nothing but
an ordinary yellow thread.

02:13:58.000 --> 02:14:02.480
It's like a golden license.

02:14:04.080 --> 02:14:08.000
Remove it and come with me.

02:14:10.200 --> 02:14:14.200
Why are you thinking so much?
It's just a display.

02:14:16.000 --> 02:14:19.720
Remove it! Remove this worthless
thing! What does it have?

02:14:21.600 --> 02:14:23.120
Do you understand
what I'm saying?

02:14:28.800 --> 02:14:31.120
'I accept this nuptial thread,'

02:14:31.800 --> 02:14:33.800
'considering the sacred
fire as the witness,'

02:14:34.520 --> 02:14:36.960
'considering God
as the witness,'

02:14:37.560 --> 02:14:39.120
'the celestial bodies
as the witness,'

02:14:39.240 --> 02:14:42.400
'considering the saints and
sages as the witness,'

02:14:43.040 --> 02:14:44.400
'I give this oath,'

02:14:45.400 --> 02:14:48.800
'that I'll hold this nuptial
thread dearer than my life.'

02:14:49.200 --> 02:14:52.280
'I'll uphold its
dignity all my life.'

02:15:03.120 --> 02:15:08.200
Dad called and said its okay if
you don't want to meet grandma.

02:15:08.400 --> 02:15:12.000
But have your breakfast and
do take your medicine.

02:15:12.080 --> 02:15:13.560
That is most important.

02:15:18.000 --> 02:15:19.800
If Chanda got used
to mother's love,

02:15:20.520 --> 02:15:23.840
..then how will I give it
to her after you leave?

02:15:25.800 --> 02:15:30.160
Today you're going to bond with
this family for a lifetime.

02:15:32.080 --> 02:15:34.520
Maya is an Indian girl with
orthodox thinking, sir.

02:15:36.560 --> 02:15:39.720
She's still in a dilemma
about the nuptial thread.

02:15:41.440 --> 02:15:44.800
She doesn't know of this new
world and the new revolution.

02:15:46.200 --> 02:15:49.280
You explained that to me
and I've understood too.

02:15:50.800 --> 02:15:54.800
Sir, I think you should do it.

02:15:55.480 --> 02:15:59.200
You remove the nuptial thread.
Do it!

02:16:06.080 --> 02:16:08.760
You are a man. What
are you afraid of?

02:16:08.840 --> 02:16:11.480
You have the right to
disobey this old tradition.

02:16:13.000 --> 02:16:14.960
Pull out this nuptial
thread from Maya's neck.

02:16:16.440 --> 02:16:18.080
So that I can take her with me.

02:16:24.600 --> 02:16:27.480
What are you thinking, sir? These
orthodox rituals are of no use!

02:16:27.760 --> 02:16:31.560
Break these bonds! Go ahead!

02:16:38.480 --> 02:16:39.240
Yes, mother.

02:16:39.640 --> 02:16:41.600
I'll do everything for
Maya's happiness.

02:16:42.640 --> 02:16:45.720
I'll fulfil all her wishes.
I promise you.

02:17:07.600 --> 02:17:08.800
No!

02:17:33.520 --> 02:17:34.280
No!

02:17:43.120 --> 02:17:44.360
This is our story, sir.

02:17:45.720 --> 02:17:48.400
The story of our country's
tradition and values.

02:17:50.560 --> 02:17:52.000
I'm not an educated man.

02:17:54.200 --> 02:17:58.480
But I do know that my lover
may become somebody's wife,

02:17:59.800 --> 02:18:02.120
..but somebody's wife
can never be my lover.

02:18:02.480 --> 02:18:05.280
The heart of an unmarried
woman is like a mirror.

02:18:07.600 --> 02:18:11.560
It reflects the one
who stands before it.

02:18:13.080 --> 02:18:17.400
But after marriage, that reflection
gets converted into an image, sir.

02:18:19.640 --> 02:18:23.200
A husband's image. Your image.

02:18:24.320 --> 02:18:25.800
This will never change.

02:18:26.400 --> 02:18:30.080
This can be the only
climax to this story.

02:18:30.840 --> 02:18:32.760
Nothing else. Never!

02:18:34.280 --> 02:18:36.360
You might find my
thinking orthodox.

02:18:37.000 --> 02:18:42.400
It is very old. But
sir, old is gold.

02:18:43.680 --> 02:18:45.560
I'll take your leave now.

02:18:46.640 --> 02:18:47.760
Goodbye, Mr. Anand.

02:18:48.600 --> 02:18:52.640
Sorry, Mrs. and Mr.
Anand. Goodbye!